\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\fs20\cf0 To create magic items, spellcasters use special feats. They invest time, money, and their own personal energy (in the form of experience points) in an item\rquote s creation.
